Package: SampleRiskRatioMultiENG
Title: Sample Size Calculation for Risk Ratio Studies
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Victor J.", "Vera-Ponce", email = "victor_jvp@hotmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package provides tools for calculating sample size in cohort studies
    using relative risk as a measure of association, considering multivariable
    analysis and logistical aspects of the study. Includes functions for sample
    size calculation considering correlation between covariables, statistical
    power evaluation, and study logistics planning.
